| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-0166 — Mass File Rename (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 961492b2-bb96-5324-8ce3-d590e5224398"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
